// {{.Name}} — scaffolded by `de project init`.
//
// Subcommands:
//
//	serve        run the service: gRPC (GRPC_ADDR, default 127.0.0.1:9090)
//	             behind a fail-closed authz interceptor, with the REST
//	             gateway on HTTP_ADDR (default :8080) — the port devedge
//	             routes the dev hostname to.
//	migrate up   converge the database schema to this build's bundled
//	             migrations (devedge's deploy hook runs this before the
//	             workload serves; local `de project up` applies migrations
//	             for you, so you rarely run it by hand).
